<text id="WB19">
    <metadata>
        <title>"The Perils of Weasel"</title>
        <author>Mamie <alph>Offield</alph></author>
        <date>1957</date>
        <publication>William Bright, <em>The Karok Language</em> (1957), pp. 208-209, Text 19</publication>
    </metadata>
    <data>
        <paragraph>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w>
                        <m id="3804">kéevniikich</m>
                    </w>
                    <w>
                        <m id="6675">vúra</m>
                    </w>
                    <w>
                        <m id="6307">uum</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="she liked">
                        <m id="6175">u</m>
                        <m id="5672">tapkûupu</m>
                        <m id="6035">ti</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="that she gamble">
                        <m id="4408">pó</m>
                        <m id="6175">o</m>
                        <m id="3288">thtii</m>
                        <m id="6035">tih</m>
                    </w>.
                </kar>
                <eng>An old woman liked to gamble.</eng>
            </s>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w gl="a man">
                        <m id="4407">pa'</m>
                        <m id="833">ávansa</m>
                    </w>
                    <w>
                        <m id="3670">káan</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="when he arrived">
                        <m id="5506">t</m>
                        <m id="5175">u</m>
                        <m id="6306">'uum</m>
                        <m id="1358">áhaak</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="she did">
                        <m id="5506">tó</m>
                        <m id="6175">o</m>
                    </w>
                    <w>
                        <m id="4823">piip</m>
                    </w>
                    "<w>
                        <m id="1745">íkamish</m>
                    </w>
                    <w>
                        <m id="1144">chími</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="let's gamble">
                        <m id="4370">nu</m>
                        <m id="3288">thtîi</m>
                        <m id="6035">ti</m>
                    </w>.
                </kar>
                <eng>When a man arrived there, she said "Son-in-law, let's gamble!"</eng>
            </s>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w>
                        <m id="7035">yakún</m>
                    </w>
                    <w>
                        <m id="5506">tá</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="I bet">
                        <m id="4349">ní</m>
                        <m id="3514">xraam</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="my child">
                        <m id="4407">pa</m>
                        <m id="4326">naní</m>
                        <m id="511">'aramah</m>
                    </w>".
                </kar>
                <eng>I'll bet my child.</eng>
            </s>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w>
                        <m id="7035">púyava</m>
                    </w>
                    <w>
                        <m id="5506">tá</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="they gamble">
                        <m id="3977">kun</m>
                        <m id="3288">íthtit</m>
                    </w>.
                </kar>
                <eng>So they gambled.</eng>
            </s>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w>
                        <m id="7035">púyava</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="when she did">
                        <m id="4408">pa</m>
                        <m id="5506">tó</m>
                        <m id="6175">o</m>
                    </w>
                    <w>
                        <m id="6939">xus</m>
                    </w>
                    "<w>
                        <m id="5506">tá</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="you beat me">
                        <m id="3737">kana</m>
                        <m id="1110">chífich</m>
                    </w>,"
                    <w>
                        <m id="3745">kári</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="her earrings">
                        <m id="4407">pa</m>
                        <m id="4260">mu</m>
                        <m id="5833">têenva</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="she did">
                        <m id="5506">tó</m>
                        <m id="6175">o</m>
                    </w>
                    <w>
                        <m id="3185">syuunkiv</m>
                    </w>.
                </kar>
                <eng>And when she thought, "I've been beaten," then she pulled off her
                    earrings.</eng>
            </s>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w gl="and thus">
                        <m id="3745">kári</m>
                        <m id="6383">va</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="with it">
                        <m id="3970">ku</m>
                        <m id="4281">mûuk</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="she did">
                        <m id="5506">tó</m>
                        <m id="6175">o</m></w>
		    <w>	
                        <m id="2138">ktir</m>
                    </w>,
                    <w>
                        <m id="573">áriim</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="knocked him down">
                        <m id="5506">t</m>
                        <m id="6175">u</m>
                        <m id="5872">thantífish</m>
                    </w>.
                </kar>
                <eng>She hit him with them, knocked him dead.</eng>
            </s>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w>
                        <m id="7035">púyava</m>
                    </w>
                    <w>
                        <m id="3969">kúkuum</m>
                    </w>
                    <w>
                        <m id="7097">yítha</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="one would arrive">
                        <m id="5506">t</m>
                        <m id="6175">u'</m>
                        <m id="6306">uum</m>
                    </w>,
                    <w>
                        <m id="3969">kúkuum</m>
                    </w>
                    <w>
                        <m id="6675">vúra</m>
                    </w>
                    <w>
                        <m id="6383">vaa</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="she would">
                        <m id="5506">tó</m>
                        <m id="6175">o</m></w>
		    <w>	
                        <m id="2733">pêer</m>
                    </w>
                    "<w>
                        <m id="1745">íkamish</m>
                    </w>
                    <w>
                        <m id="1144">chími</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="let's gamble">
                        <m id="4370">nu</m>
                        <m id="3288">thtîi</m>
                        <m id="6035">ti</m>
                    </w>."
                </kar>
                <eng>So again one would arrive, again she would say, "Son in law, let's
                    gamble!"</eng>
            </s>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w>
                        <m id="1096">chavúra</m>
                    </w>
                    <w>
                        <m id="5541">táay</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="she did">
                        <m id="5506">tó</m>
                        <m id="6175">o</m></w>
	            <w>
                        <m id="3580">ykar</m>
                    </w>.
                </kar>
                <eng>Finally she killed a lot.</eng>
            </s>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w>
                        <m id="3748">kári xás</m>
                    </w>
                    <w>
                        <m id="6307">uum</m>
                    </w>
                    <w>
                        <m id="3752">káru</m>
                    </w>
                    <w>
                        <m id="2961">ishímfir</m>
                    </w>,
                    <w>
                        <m id="34">âanaxus</m>
                    </w>.
                </kar>
                <eng>And Weasel was tough, too.</eng>
            </s>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w>
                        <m id="3748">kári xás</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="he thought">
                        <m id="6175">u</m>
                        <m id="6939">xus</m>
                    </w>
                    "<w>
                        <m id="6042">tîi</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="I go look for her">
                        <m id="3735">kan</m>
                        <m id="2570">imús</m>
                        <m id="501">an</m>
                    </w>."
                </kar>
                <eng>And he thought, "Let me go see her!"</eng>
            </s>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w>
                        <m id="3748">kári xás</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="she said">
                        <m id="6175">u</m>
                        <m id="4823">piip</m>
                    </w>
                    "<w>
                        <m id="1745">íkamish</m>
                    </w>
                    <w>
                        <m id="1144">chími</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="let's gamble">
                        <m id="4370">nu</m>
                        <m id="3288">thtîi</m>
                        <m id="6035">ti</m>
                    </w>."
                </kar>
                <eng>And she said, "Son-in-law, let's gamble."</eng>
            </s>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w>
                        <m id="6174">ta'ítam</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="they gambled">
                        <m id="3977">kun</m>
                        <m id="3288">ithtít</m>
                        <m id="1378">aheen</m>
                    </w>.
                </kar>
                <eng>So they gambled.</eng>
            </s>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w>
                        <m id="3748">kári xás</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="the old woman">
                        <m id="4407">pa</m>
                        <m id="3804">kéevniikich</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="she sang">
                        <m id="5506">t</m>
                        <m id="6175">u'</m>
                        <m id="561">árihish</m>
                    </w>,
                    <w gl="she sang">
                        <m id="5506">t</m>
                        <m id="6175">u</m>
                        <m id="4511">pakúriihva</m>
                    </w>,
                    "<w>
                        <m id="34">âanaxus</m>
                    </w>
                    <w> itvaratvárah</w>."
                </kar>
                <eng>Then the old woman sang, she sang "âanaxus itvaratvárah."</eng>
            </s>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w>
                        <m id="3748">kári xás</m>
                    </w>
                    <w>
                        <m id="34">âanaxus</m>
                    </w>
                    <w>
                        <m id="6307">uum</m>
                    </w>
                    <w>
                        <m id="3752">káru</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="he sang">
                        <m id="5506">t</m>
                        <m id="6175">u</m>
                        <m id="4511">pakúriihva</m>
                    </w>, "<w>
                        <m id="3804">kéevniikich</m>
                    </w>
                    <w> tiiptíip'aahrishuk </w>." </kar>
                <eng>And Weasel sang, too, "kéevniikich tiiptíip'aahrishuk."</eng>
            </s>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w>
                        <m id="7035">púyava</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="the old woman">
                        <m id="4407">pa</m>
                        <m id="3804">kéevniikich</m>
                    </w>
                    <w>
                        <m id="5506">tá</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="she was beaten">
                        <m id="3977">kun</m>
                        <m id="1110">chífich</m>
                    </w>.
                </kar>
                <eng>Then the old woman was beaten.</eng>
            </s>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w>
                        <m id="3748">kári xás</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="her earring">
                        <m id="4407">pa</m>
                        <m id="4260">mu</m>
                        <m id="5833">têenva</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="she pulled off">
                        <m id="6175">ú</m>
                        <m id="3185">syuunkiv</m>
                    </w>.
                </kar>
                <eng>And she pulled off her earring.</eng>
            </s>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w>
                        <m id="3748">kári xás</m>
                    </w>
                    <w>
                        <m id="6383">vaa</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="with it">
                        <m id="3970">ku</m>
                        <m id="4281">mûuk</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="she hit">
                        <m id="6175">ú</m>
                        <m id="2138">ktir</m>
                    </w>.
                </kar>
                <eng>And she hit at him with it.</eng>
            </s>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w>
                        <m id="34">âanaxus</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="he ducked">
                        <m id="6175">ú</m>
                        <m id="3140">svay</m>
                    </w>,
                    <w gl="she missed">
                        <m id="6175">u</m>
                        <m id="5865">thanfírip</m>
                    </w>.
                </kar>
                <eng>Weasel ducked, she missed him.</eng>
            </s>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w>
                        <m id="3969">kúkuum</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="they gambled">
                        <m id="3977">kun</m>
                        <m id="4406">p</m>
                        <m id="3288">íthtit</m>
                    </w>.
                </kar>
                <eng>They gambled again.</eng>
            </s>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w>
                        <m id="411">ápap</m>
                    </w>
                    <w>
                        <m id="3978">kúna</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="she pulled off">
                        <m id="6175">ú</m>
                        <m id="3185">syuunkiv</m>
                    </w>.
                </kar>
                <eng>She pulled off (the earring) on the other side.</eng>
            </s>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w>
                        <m id="6383">vaa</m>
                    </w>
                    <w>
                        <m id="3978">kúna</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="with it">
                        <m id="3970">ku</m>
                        <m id="4281">mûuk</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="she hit">
                        <m id="6175">ú</m>
                        <m id="2138">ktir</m>
                    </w>.
                </kar>
                <eng>She hit at him with it in turn.</eng>
            </s>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w>
                        <m id="3969">kúkuum</m>
                    </w>
                    <w>
                        <m id="6675">vúra</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="she missed">
                        <m id="6175">u</m>
                        <m id="5865">thanfírip</m>
                    </w>.
                </kar>
                <eng>Again she missed him.</eng>
            </s>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w>
                        <m id="3748">kári xás</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="she said">
                        <m id="6175">u</m>
                        <m id="4823">píip</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="the old woman">
                        <m id="4407">pa</m>
                        <m id="3804">kéevniikich</m>
                    </w>,
                    "<w>
                        <m id="1192">chôora</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="my pet">
                        <m id="4326">nani</m>
                        <m id="3848">kinínaasich</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="bring down">
                        <m id="2144">iktûunih</m>
                        <m id="1419">i</m>
                    </w>.
                </kar>
                <eng>Then the old woman said, "Let's go, bring down my pet.</eng>
            </s>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w>
                        <m id="7157">yukún</m>
                    </w>
                    <w>
                        <m id="6381">vaa</m>
                    </w>
                    <w>
                        <m id="3670">káan</m>
                    </w>
		    <w><m id="7273">á'</m></w>
                    <w gl="he is sitting">
                        <m id="6175">u</m>
                        <m id="1711">'íithra</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="slippery tree top">
                        <m id="4274">murax</m>
                        <m id="2682">'ipaha</m>
                        <m id="2697">'ípan</m>
                    </w>."
                </kar>
                <eng>He's up there at the top of a slippery tree."</eng>
            </s>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w>
                        <m id="3748">kári xás</m>
                    </w>
                    <w>
                        <m id="34">âanaxus</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="he climbed up">
                        <m id="6175">u</m>
                        <m id="6625">vôoruraa</m>
                    </w>.
                </kar>
                <eng>So Weasel climbed up.</eng>
            </s>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w>
                        <m id="3748">kári xás</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="he brought down">
                        <m id="6175">u</m>
                        <m id="2144">ktûunih</m>
                    </w>.
                </kar>
                <eng>And he brought it down.</eng>
            </s>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w>
                        <m id="7038">yánava</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="long snake children">
                        <m id="450">apsunxarah</m>
                        <m id="6132">túnviiv</m>
                    </w>.
                </kar>
                <eng>He saw it was baby long-snakes.</eng>
            </s>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w>
                        <m id="3748">kári xás</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="he said">
                        <m id="6175">u</m>
                        <m id="2733">pêer</m>
                    </w>
                    "<w>
                        <m id="4132">mâa</m>
                    </w>
                    <w>
                        <m id="4715">páy</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="your pets">
                        <m id="4407">pa</m>
                        <m id="4238">mi</m>
                        <m id="3848">kinínaasich</m>
                    </w>."
                </kar>
                <eng>And he said, "Here's your pets."</eng>
            </s>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w>
                        <m id="3748">kári xás</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="she ran">
                        <m id="6175">ú</m>
                        <m id="2195">kvip</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="the old woman">
                        <m id="4407">pa</m>
                        <m id="3804">kéevniikich</m>
                    </w>.
                </kar>
                <eng>And then the old woman ran.</eng>
            </s>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w>
                        <m id="3748">kári xás</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="long snake">
                        <m id="450">apsunxarah</m>
                        <m id="1670">'îin</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="they ate">
                        <m id="3977">kun</m>
                        <m id="814">'av</m>
                    </w>.
                </kar>
                <eng>But she was eaten by a long snake</eng>
            </s>
        </paragraph>
    </data>
